493
00:44:27,848 --> 00:44:28,815
But wait.

494
00:44:29,049 --> 00:44:33,645
You know Lois is doing that interview
with Superman about his peace mission.

495
00:44:33,887 --> 00:44:38,085
Well, I was thinking the four of us
can get together and have high tea.

496
00:44:38,325 --> 00:44:39,758
It's very chic.

497
00:44:39,960 --> 00:44:42,895
- Can you hand me those weights, Clark?
- Excuse me.

498
00:44:43,931 --> 00:44:44,955
Wait a minute, Lacy.

499
00:44:45,432 --> 00:44:49,732
Come early. The view is so romantic
